{"tid":1495971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【最後3日】查選民登記冊","createTime":"2019-08-22T09:52:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T13:34:04.000Z","uid":131278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a24b8748d26918a1980984c8375f297e8371d80f","tid":1495971,"uid":131278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T09:52:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www1.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/mob/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fmob%2F&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGIcF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=12699563\" target=\"_blank\">https://www1.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/mob/</a><br />\n<br />\n<em>2019年臨時選民登記冊已於2019年8月1日發表。<br />\n<br />\n你可以使用本網站搜尋資料以確定自己是否一名已登記選民，以及查閱你在上述選民登記冊上的現有登記資料。就編製下一份選民登記冊而言，如果你已提交登記申請或更新登記資料，而選舉事務處亦已成功處理有關申請，你亦可查閱你的最新登記資料。</em><br />\n<br />\n<strong>麻煩大家不嫌其煩重新check吓有無被dq,另外新登記人士麻煩check吓是否已成功登記<br />\n<br />\n<ins>2019年11月24日（星期日）區議會選舉</ins> <br />\n麻煩大家記得預留當日投票！踢走晒民建聯！</strong>"},{"pid":"00edff0ac38bb2d31c1ab5387c530acd3e9f56a7","tid":1495971,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T10:14:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大大聲傳出去啊！！！<br />\n【我宣布】中秋開始罷工罷到支爆為止<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1495391\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1495391</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wERJGgC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwERJGgC.jpg&h=7d6f3fa7&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zA2HWPY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzA2HWPY.jpg&h=fa97f1b3&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wEtzNWE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwEtzNWE.jpg&h=b642e83c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98284885b9fc9dd76b5dfddf943ce61a81255212","tid":1495971,"uid":293029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT